# Attack 07 – Credential Dumping Simulation

## Objective

Simulate credential dumping techniques in a safe lab environment.

## Attack

Attempted LSASS memory dumping using:

- rundll32.exe
- comsvcs.dll MiniDump

Microsoft Defender blocked execution.

## Detection

PowerShell activity and process creation events were captured by Wazuh.

## MITRE ATT&CK

- T1003.001 – LSASS Memory

## Investigation

Reviewed PowerShell execution, Defender response, and Sysmon logs.

## Outcome

Credential dumping attempt was prevented and recorded.
